  "title": "(TRAVEL OPPS)(FRESH GRADS) Entry Level Sales and Marketing",
  "description": "<p>If staring at a screen all day isn’t your thing 💻❌<br />but you’re also not trying to do manual labour 😅<br />this might be a decent middle ground 👀✨</p><p>At <strong>Thrive Organization</strong>, we do face-to-face marketing for brands 🤝<br />It’s a <strong>full-time role</strong> where you interact with people, work with a team, and learn practical skills — without being stuck in an office.</p><p><strong>What You’ll Do 👇</strong><br />• Talk to people & explain products 🗣️<br />• Help out at booths, events & activations 🎪<br />• Work alongside a team (not solo) 👊<br />• Build communication & people skills 📢</p><p><strong>Who This Suits 👀</strong><br />• Fresh grads / first-job era 🎓<br />• Prefer people > screens<br />• Want experience without crazy pressure<br />• Okay with being on-site, not office-bound</p><p>Training provided. No experience needed.<br />If you’re looking for something different — but still manageable — start with <strong>Thrive Organization</strong> 🌱</p>",
